WEBVTT

00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:14.700
Mayuri?

00:00:16.410 --> 00:00:20.830
You were sent here by a time machine.

00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:23.080
Is that you, Mayuri?

00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:26.080
Mayushii has looked for Okarin

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:33.010
in many, many, many world lines, chasing him.

00:00:33.010 --> 00:00:34.510
Mayuri?

00:00:34.510 --> 00:00:36.680
You could say that the Okarin here

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:40.100
is one of many Okarins, but you could say

00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:41.930
he's the original Okarin.

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:44.560
You could also say the Mayushii here

00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:48.360
is one of many Mayushiis,

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:50.190
but that she's the original too.

00:00:51.110 --> 00:00:52.110
And so,

00:00:52.110 --> 00:00:55.860
I think Okarin and Mayushii are gonna die here.

00:00:57.700 --> 00:00:59.030
But I believe

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:03.290
our legacy will carry on to the Okarin and Mayushii in Akihabara,

00:01:03.290 --> 00:01:05.080
70 million years from now.

00:01:06.290 --> 00:01:07.330
So...

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:09.210
it's okay.

